data.name: ReadCsePersonSupported

data.name: ReadDebtAdjustment1
data.value: select OBG_GENERATED_ID, CSP_NUMBER, CPA_TYPE, OB_TRN_ID, OB_TRN_TYP, OB_TRN_AMT, DEBT_ADJ_TYP, DEB_ADJ_DT, CREATED_TMST, CSP_SUP_NUMBER, CPA_SUP_TYPE, OTY_TYPE from CKT_OB_TRN where @cpaType = CPA_TYPE and @cspNumber = CSP_NUMBER and DEBT_ADJ_TYP = 'D' and DEB_ADJ_DT > @debAdjDt and OB_TRN_TYP = 'DA'

data.name: ReadDebtAdjustment2
data.value: select T1.OBG_GENERATED_ID, T1.CSP_NUMBER, T1.CPA_TYPE, T1.OB_TRN_ID, T1.OB_TRN_TYP, T1.OB_TRN_AMT, T1.DEBT_ADJ_TYP, T1.DEB_ADJ_DT, T1.CREATED_TMST, T1.CSP_SUP_NUMBER, T1.CPA_SUP_TYPE, T1.OTY_TYPE from CKT_OB_TRN T1 with(readuncommitted) where @otyType = T1.OTY_TYPE and @obgGeneratedId = T1.OBG_GENERATED_ID and @cspNumber = T1.CSP_NUMBER and @cpaType = T1.CPA_TYPE and T1.DEB_ADJ_DT > @debAdjDt and T1.OB_TRN_TYP = 'DA' and exists ( select * from CKT_OB_TRN_RLN T2 with(readuncommitted) where T1.OTY_TYPE = T2.OTY_TYPE_SECONDARY and T1.OB_TRN_TYP = T2.OTR_TYPE and T1.OB_TRN_ID = T2.OTR_GENERATED_ID and T1.CPA_TYPE = T2.CPA_TYPE and T1.CSP_NUMBER = T2.CSP_NUMBER and T1.OBG_GENERATED_ID = T2.OBG_GENERATED_ID and @otyTypePrimary = T2.OTY_TYPE_PRIMARY and @otrPType = T2.OTR_P_TYPE and @otrPGeneratedId = T2.OTR_P_GENERATED_ID and @cpaPType = T2.CPA_P_TYPE and @cspPNumber = T2.CSP_P_NUMBER and @obgPGeneratedId = T2.OBG_P_GENERATED_ID )

data.name: ReadDebtObligationObligationTypeDebtDetail1
data.value: select T1.OBG_GENERATED_ID, T1.CSP_NUMBER, T1.CPA_TYPE, T1.OB_TRN_ID, T1.OB_TRN_TYP, T1.OB_TRN_AMT, T1.CREATED_TMST, T1.CSP_SUP_NUMBER, T1.CPA_SUP_TYPE, T1.OTY_TYPE, T2.PRIM_SEC_CD, T2.CREATED_TMST, T2.ORD_TYP_CD, T3.DEBT_TYP_CD, T3.DEBT_TYP_CLASS, T4.DUE_DT, T4.BAL_DUE_AMT, T4.CVRD_PRD_START_DT, T4.PRECNVRSN_PGM_CD, T4.CREATED_TMST from CKT_OB_TYPE T3 with(readuncommitted) join CKT_OBLIGATION T2 with(readuncommitted) join CKT_OB_TRN T1 with(readuncommitted) on @cpaType = T2.CPA_TYPE and @cspNumber = T2.CSP_NUMBER and T2.DTY_GENERATED_ID = T1.OTY_TYPE and T2.OB_ID = T1.OBG_GENERATED_ID and T2.CSP_NUMBER = T1.CSP_NUMBER and T2.CPA_TYPE = T1.CPA_TYPE and @cpaSupType = T1.CPA_SUP_TYPE and @cspSupNumber = T1.CSP_SUP_NUMBER and T2.PRIM_SEC_CD <> 'S' and T2.ORD_TYP_CD <> 'I' and T1.CREATED_TMST <= @createdTmst and T1.OB_TRN_TYP = 'DE' on T3.DEBT_TYP_ID = T2.DTY_GENERATED_ID join CKT_DEBT_DTL T4 with(readuncommitted) on T4.BAL_DUE_AMT > 0 and T1.OTY_TYPE = T4.OTY_TYPE and T1.OBG_GENERATED_ID = T4.OBG_GENERATED_ID and T1.OB_TRN_TYP = T4.OTR_TYPE and T1.OB_TRN_ID = T4.OTR_GENERATED_ID and T1.CPA_TYPE = T4.CPA_TYPE and T1.CSP_NUMBER = T4.CSP_NUMBER and ( T3.DEBT_TYP_CLASS = 'A' and T4.DUE_DT < dateadd(month, - 1, cast(@date as date)) or T3.DEBT_TYP_CLASS in ('M', 'N') )

data.name: ReadDebtObligationObligationTypeDebtDetail2
data.value: select T1.OBG_GENERATED_ID, T1.CSP_NUMBER, T1.CPA_TYPE, T1.OB_TRN_ID, T1.OB_TRN_TYP, T1.OB_TRN_AMT, T1.CREATED_TMST, T1.CSP_SUP_NUMBER, T1.CPA_SUP_TYPE, T1.OTY_TYPE, T2.PRIM_SEC_CD, T2.CREATED_TMST, T2.ORD_TYP_CD, T3.DEBT_TYP_CD, T3.DEBT_TYP_CLASS, T4.DUE_DT, T4.BAL_DUE_AMT, T4.CVRD_PRD_START_DT, T4.PRECNVRSN_PGM_CD, T4.CREATED_TMST from CKT_OB_TYPE T3 with(readuncommitted) join CKT_OBLIGATION T2 with(readuncommitted) join CKT_OB_TRN T1 with(readuncommitted) on @cpaType = T2.CPA_TYPE and @cspNumber = T2.CSP_NUMBER and T2.DTY_GENERATED_ID = T1.OTY_TYPE and T2.OB_ID = T1.OBG_GENERATED_ID and T2.CSP_NUMBER = T1.CSP_NUMBER and T2.CPA_TYPE = T1.CPA_TYPE and @cpaSupType = T1.CPA_SUP_TYPE and @cspSupNumber = T1.CSP_SUP_NUMBER and T2.PRIM_SEC_CD <> 'S' and T2.ORD_TYP_CD <> 'I' and T1.CREATED_TMST <= @createdTmst and T1.OB_TRN_TYP = 'DE' on T3.DEBT_TYP_ID = T2.DTY_GENERATED_ID join CKT_DEBT_DTL T4 with(readuncommitted) on T4.BAL_DUE_AMT = 0 and T1.OTY_TYPE = T4.OTY_TYPE and T1.OBG_GENERATED_ID = T4.OBG_GENERATED_ID and T1.OB_TRN_TYP = T4.OTR_TYPE and T1.OB_TRN_ID = T4.OTR_GENERATED_ID and T1.CPA_TYPE = T4.CPA_TYPE and T1.CSP_NUMBER = T4.CSP_NUMBER and ( T3.DEBT_TYP_CLASS = 'A' and T4.DUE_DT < dateadd(month, - 1, cast(@date as date)) or T3.DEBT_TYP_CLASS in ('M', 'N') ) where exists ( select * from CKT_COLLECTION T5 with(readuncommitted) where T1.OTY_TYPE = T5.OTY_ID and T1.OB_TRN_TYP = T5.OTR_TYPE and T1.OB_TRN_ID = T5.OTR_ID and T1.CPA_TYPE = T5.CPA_TYPE and T1.CSP_NUMBER = T5.CSP_NUMBER and T1.OBG_GENERATED_ID = T5.OBG_ID and (T5.APPLIED_TO_CD in ('C', 'A')) and T5.ADJ_IND = 'N' and T5.CREATED_TMST > @createdTmst )

data.name: ReadDebtObligationObligationTypeDebtDetail3
data.value: select T1.OBG_GENERATED_ID, T1.CSP_NUMBER, T1.CPA_TYPE, T1.OB_TRN_ID, T1.OB_TRN_TYP, T1.OB_TRN_AMT, T1.CREATED_TMST, T1.CSP_SUP_NUMBER, T1.CPA_SUP_TYPE, T1.OTY_TYPE, T2.PRIM_SEC_CD, T2.CREATED_TMST, T2.ORD_TYP_CD, T3.DEBT_TYP_CD, T3.DEBT_TYP_CLASS, T4.DUE_DT, T4.BAL_DUE_AMT, T4.CVRD_PRD_START_DT, T4.PRECNVRSN_PGM_CD, T4.CREATED_TMST from CKT_OB_TYPE T3 with(readuncommitted) join CKT_OBLIGATION T2 with(readuncommitted) join CKT_OB_TRN T1 with(readuncommitted) on @cpaType = T2.CPA_TYPE and @cspNumber = T2.CSP_NUMBER and T2.DTY_GENERATED_ID = T1.OTY_TYPE and T2.OB_ID = T1.OBG_GENERATED_ID and T2.CSP_NUMBER = T1.CSP_NUMBER and T2.CPA_TYPE = T1.CPA_TYPE and @cpaSupType = T1.CPA_SUP_TYPE and @cspSupNumber = T1.CSP_SUP_NUMBER and T2.PRIM_SEC_CD <> 'S' and T2.ORD_TYP_CD <> 'I' and T1.CREATED_TMST <= @createdTmst and T1.OB_TRN_TYP = 'DE' on T3.DEBT_TYP_ID = T2.DTY_GENERATED_ID join CKT_DEBT_DTL T4 with(readuncommitted) on T4.BAL_DUE_AMT = 0 and T1.OTY_TYPE = T4.OTY_TYPE and T1.OBG_GENERATED_ID = T4.OBG_GENERATED_ID and T1.OB_TRN_TYP = T4.OTR_TYPE and T1.OB_TRN_ID = T4.OTR_GENERATED_ID and T1.CPA_TYPE = T4.CPA_TYPE and T1.CSP_NUMBER = T4.CSP_NUMBER and ( T3.DEBT_TYP_CLASS = 'A' and T4.DUE_DT < dateadd(month, - 1, cast(@date as date)) or T3.DEBT_TYP_CLASS in ('M', 'N') ) where exists ( select * from CKT_OB_TRN T6 with(readuncommitted) join CKT_OB_TRN_RLN T5 with(readuncommitted) on T6.OTY_TYPE = T5.OTY_TYPE_SECONDARY and T6.OB_TRN_TYP = T5.OTR_TYPE and T6.OB_TRN_ID = T5.OTR_GENERATED_ID and T6.CPA_TYPE = T5.CPA_TYPE and T6.CSP_NUMBER = T5.CSP_NUMBER and T6.OBG_GENERATED_ID = T5.OBG_GENERATED_ID and T6.DEBT_ADJ_TYP = 'D' and T6.DEB_ADJ_DT > @date and T6.OB_TRN_TYP = 'DA' where T1.OTY_TYPE = T5.OTY_TYPE_PRIMARY and T1.OB_TRN_TYP = T5.OTR_P_TYPE and T1.OB_TRN_ID = T5.OTR_P_GENERATED_ID and T1.CPA_TYPE = T5.CPA_P_TYPE and T1.CSP_NUMBER = T5.CSP_P_NUMBER and T1.OBG_GENERATED_ID = T5.OBG_P_GENERATED_ID and T2.DTY_GENERATED_ID = T6.OTY_TYPE and T2.OB_ID = T6.OBG_GENERATED_ID and T2.CSP_NUMBER = T6.CSP_NUMBER and T2.CPA_TYPE = T6.CPA_TYPE )

data.name: ReadObligationRln
data.value: select OBG_GENERATED_ID, CSP_NUMBER, CPA_TYPE, OBG_F_GENERATED_ID, CSP_F_NUMBER, CPA_F_TYPE, ORR_GENERATED_ID, OTY_SECOND_ID, OTY_FIRST_ID, OB_RLN_DSC from CKT_OBG_RLN with(readuncommitted) where @otyFirstId = OTY_FIRST_ID and @obgFGeneratedId = OBG_F_GENERATED_ID and @cspFNumber = CSP_F_NUMBER and @cpaFType = CPA_F_TYPE

data.name: ReadObligorCsePersonCollection
data.value: select * from ( select CSP_NUMBER, TYPE from CKT_CSE_PERSON_ACC with(readuncommitted) where CSP_NUMBER > @cspNumber and TYPE = 'R' ) S1 outer apply ( select top(1) COLL_ID, APPLIED_TO_CD, COLL_DT, ADJ_IND, CONCURRENT_IND, CRT_TYPE, CST_ID, CRV_ID, CRD_ID, OBG_ID, CSP_NUMBER, CPA_TYPE, OTR_ID, OTR_TYPE, OTY_ID, COLL_ADJ_DT, CREATED_TMST, OB_TRN_AMT, PGM_APPLD_TO from CKT_COLLECTION where (APPLIED_TO_CD in ('C', 'A')) and ADJ_IND = 'N' and CREATED_TMST > @createdTmst and S1.TYPE = CPA_TYPE and S1.CSP_NUMBER = CSP_NUMBER and OTR_TYPE = 'DE' ) S2 order by S1.CSP_NUMBER
